Paper: hep-th/9708106

Date: 1997-08-20

Title: Geometric Classification of Topological Quantum Phases

Authors: C. Kohler

Comments: 10 pages, Latex

On the basis of the principle that topological quantum phases arise from thescattering around space-time defects in higher dimensional unification, ageometric model is presented that associates with each quantum phase an elementof a transformation group.